---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Hey — I'm Ko‑Hsin"
	description="A friendly corner of the web for modern frontend, full‑stack notes, and experiments."
>
	<section class="about">
		<p>
			Welcome to my little internet workspace. I’m a frontend‑leaning engineer who spends a lot of time with Angular, TypeScript, and performance‑minded UI. This site is where I share things I’ve learned, ship small experiments, and write the guides I wish existed when I got stuck.
		</p>

		<h2>What you’ll find here</h2>
		<ul class="bullets">
			<li>Practical how‑tos and deep‑dives (no fluff, lots of code).</li>
			<li>Front‑end architecture, API design, and auth done right.</li>
			<li>Notes from building real apps and tooling in the wild.</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Tech I enjoy</h2>
		<ul class="tags">
			<li>Angular</li>
			<li>TypeScript</li>
			<li>RxJS</li>
			<li>Astro</li>
			<li>Node.js</li>
			<li>PostgreSQL</li>
			<li>Prisma</li>
			<li>Docker</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Elsewhere</h2>
		<p>
			• GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/liangk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/liangk</a><br />
			• X/Twitter: <a href="https://x.com/kohsinliang" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@kohsinliang</a><br />
			• Say hi: <a href="mailto:hello@stackinsight.dev">hello@stackinsight.dev</a>
		</p>
	</section>

	<style>
		.about { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
		.bullets { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
		.tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: .25rem 0 0; }
		.tags li { background: #eef1f4; color: rgb(var(--gray-dark)); padding: .35rem .6rem; border-radius: 999px; font-size: .9rem; }
		a { color: rgb(var(--accent)); text-decoration: none; }
		a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
	</style>
</Layout>
